Class Validate

  • java.lang.Object
    • Validate

  • public abstract class Validate
extends java.lang.Object
    Validate Provides methods and attributes for validation of various strings and entries processed in the back-end. This is a static class, and therefore must be declared as abstract.
    Author:
    Jonathan Gillett, Daniel Smullen, Rayan Alfaheid
